BTW, on the main topic, I consider any unasked for attacking to be extremely rude.  I never help anyone unless they &quot;/yell&quot;.  I will often say, &quot;/yell if you need help&quot; to those that look like they're in danger, but that's it.  This is probaly due to my habbit for starting fights at 50% hp and taking them down to 5-10% as a matter of course when solo'ing.  It's extremely irritating, not to mention a waste of time and plat (bandages), when some newbie runs over and &quot;saves me&quot;.  Ya gotta thank 'em for trying to be nice, but damn it sure pisses me off.<br>
